column3: This document provides high-level tracking of COVID-19 testing at CHC.

Daily updates Monday - Friday during 9:30 AM Campus Response Team meeting.  Friday and weekend numbers are reported on Monday; all other days have a 1-day reporting lag.  Results from tests sent to external labs are reported back on the day the test was taken.

- Rapid tests are typically administered and resulted the same day
- Tests sent to external labs are reported on the day that results are received
